  "name": "Morrison COU1 \u2014 CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (coverage-gap variant)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). Validation activities cover nominal flow-speed combinations; edge-case operating points are not included in the validation dataset.",
