      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Numerical solver error beyond discretization is not required to be separately assessed at Model Risk Level 2. Residual convergence to 1e-5 confirmed for all simulation cases as a minimum quality check."
    },
    {
